Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Fluttershy, it'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing fun about dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary, yes.\NFun, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, the great dragon migration\Nhappens only once in a generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really wanna pass up\Na chance like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw Fluttershy,\Nwe just don't want you to miss out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss out on what? Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Big, scaly, fire-breathing dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but... no thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Fluttershy, I watched that\Nboring butterfly migration with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so now it's your turn to watch\Nthe dragon migration with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess\NI'll let you off the hook this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 2 | Episode 21\NDragon Quest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Timed by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think we missed them, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a little early,\Nand I'm glad we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, we can watch\Nevery moment of the migration
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without bringing any unwanted\Nattention to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\NAm I the toast of the trench or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be toast alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dragons see you\Nparading around in that getup...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You look very nice, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But could you maybe look nice\Ndown here in the trench with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice is an understatement.\NI look fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says camouflage has to be drab?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, maties!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty lame move.\NIs that all they've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya think of that move,\NRainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think they're lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The word 'fierce' comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And 'formidable'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And 'super-duper scary'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Us dragons are definitely\Na force to be reckoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the scariest aprons\NI've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with wearing an apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be laughing when you spill\Nblueberries all over your scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Feathers. That's one tough stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One tough stain against one lame dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave him alone, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's style is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have\Nto look like other dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or act like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My little Spikey-wikey\Nis perfect the way he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't act like other dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would you want to, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you've got something those dreadfully\Nfierce dragons can only dream of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The cutest widdle chubby cheeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute?! Dragons aren't\Nsupposed to be cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie, you are turning\Nthe most delightful shade of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It it is most becoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't he adorable\Nwhen he waddles off in anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Waddle?! Arrrgggh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last time, Spike,\Nyou were given to me as an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who found you,\Nor where they found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? That's all you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't tell me anything\Nabout who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I need answers!\NI feel like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at a complete stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we do\Nsome late-night research?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See what we can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!\NI'm sure we can find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in this one either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all about dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! It's hard to believe, but ponies\Nknow next to nothing about dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently they're too rare and too scary\Nto try to talk to us or study!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if dragons cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna discover who I am\Nif it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya wanna join us for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great.\NI'm famished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me out.\NI've gotta get an early start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An early start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm going on\Na quest of self-discovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to learn what it means\Nto be a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only way I'm gonna do that\Nis to join the dragon migration!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, that's nonsense talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're a dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but those dragons mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're big, and tough, and scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm small, and meek...\Nand I like to wear aprons. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why I need\Nto spend time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is that\Nyou could get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, this time I really do have\Nto agree with Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want those big, ugly,\Nnasty dragons to hurt one little scale
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,on your cutsey-wutsey head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, do something!\NStop him before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NGive it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you think he should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Spike. I couldn't\Nanswer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My books couldn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you want\Nto look elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly believe you need\Nto go on this quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have no right to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I still say you're nutty, but hey,\NI've done lots of nutty things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,\NI guess this is goodbye, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait to hear about it,\Nwhen you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we hope your trip-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-your quest answers some of\Nyour pesky "who am I" questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everypony. I know it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Spikey-wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We have faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're following him, right?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,\Nteenage dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's more my speed. And size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nwe'll never pass for a real dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pish-posh! This costume is fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my finer creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never pass if they hear\Nthree voices coming out of one dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on,\Nlet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hi.\NI'm Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure your name\Nis Spike and not Shrimp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's Spike! I'm not,\NI mean, I'm sure about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You look more like Peewee to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, come on, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone, or he might fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, uh, if he had any wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You fly in on your mommy's back\Nduring the migration?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, can't you see\Nbaby Spike just hatched?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he still sucks his claw at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't sucked my claw in months!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well if you weren't just hatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how come we haven't seen\Nyou around before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, y'see, I live in Ponyville and-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville? That explains it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew there was something\Nvaguely pony-ish about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know any better,\NI'd say you were part pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me? I'm not part pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all dragon, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you're a pony\Nin a dragon costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A pony in a dragon costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahah... yeah... hilarious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a real dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well... how?\N- By acting like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's up for a little belching contest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can beat that, Peewee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From the desk of Princess Celestia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Spike, please... Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this, guys! Spike's penpals with\Na namby-pamby pony princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he just throw that away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That letter could be something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't worry about that now,\NTwilight, we're here to help Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to disrespect\NPrincess Celestia that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tail wrestling is more your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old tail wrestling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let little Spikey-wikey\Nwrestle one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get clobbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenge Spike to a tail wrestle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's Crackle's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That would explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, little Spike!\NMaybe you are a dragon after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Maybe I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, I can't believe\Nyour silly plan actually worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a little cocky, huh?\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about you wrestle... him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So Spike, you haven't exactly proven\Nyourself as a dragon yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I get an A for effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how you do\Nin this next contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,King of the hoard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,King of the ho-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is another\Nfail for you, little Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't wait to watch you fail\Nat lava cannonball too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever makes the biggest lava splash\Nis the ultimate dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's on his own this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You afraid the lava would hurt\Nyour soft pony hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I... that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, dude, that was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony could live through\Na belly flop like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one tough little dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, by belly flopping so hard,\Nyou have proven yourself worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby dub you 'rookie dragon'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And will now perform\Nthe initiation ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's party dragon style!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, was that a great party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, huh?\NMaybe by Ponyville standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with us, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We still got plenty to teach you\Nabout being a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.\NThe way I feel right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hang out with you guys forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spikey-wikey is going to stay\Nwith these awful dragons? Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've stopped him back\Nat the library when I had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Rainbow Dash, this is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I encouraged him to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, Spike, I think you just might\Nbe ready for a real dragon raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a nest full of phoenix eggs nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're gonna swipe 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you totally psyched\Nto go on this raid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then. Let's fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry guys! Guess I'll meet you\Nback here at the crater!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After the whole raid thing's over?\NWe'll totally hang then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they took Spike!\NWe've gotta go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, stop! We can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're ruining my fabulous costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we gotta help Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're just gonna have to hoof it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Spike,\Nsince you're a rookie dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to lure the parents\Naway from the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... lucky me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well go on, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mr and Mrs Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping I could have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you\Nsome questions actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't got all day, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you bird brains! Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The eggs have hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We take the hatchlings, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They got away! I hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the raid wasn't\Na total waste after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you\Nwaiting for, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Smash the egg?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, throw it on the ground\Nas hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash it! Smash it! Smash it!\NSmash it! Smash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's just a defenseless egg,\Nlike I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not gonna let you hurt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you say?\N- I said, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No one says no to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's gonna lay a claw on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting's not really my thing,\NI'm more into fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll rip you to pieces if you touch\None scale on his cute little head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, are these namby-pamby ponies\Nyour friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are. And they're better friends\Nthan you could ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't back off,\Nyou'll see what us ponies do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when confronted by\Na huge group of jerky dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close one. Thanks you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. What are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more than friends.\NYou're my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Princess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing the great dragon migration made me\Nwonder what it meant to be a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I realize that who I am\Nis not the same as what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been born a dragon,\Nbut Equestria and my pony friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,have taught me how to be kind,\Nloyal, and true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to call Ponyville my home,\Nand to have my pony friends as my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours truly, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome to the family, Peewee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with me, I've got plenty\Nto teach you about being a pony.
